name: wavWRLD presents wavROOM feat. Jadyn Violet

metadata.name: wavWRLD presents: wavROOM experience feat Jadyn Violet
metadata.description:
The wavROOM experiences are curated intimate performances only open to collectors of that artist. Starting off 1-of-7 performances with the king of the underground Jadyn Violet.

It will be the first live music performance minted on the blockchain.

Partnering with Reveel x Glass.xyz to record & mint the performances.

Video by Glass
Recorded, Mixed, & Mastered by Invictus @theoginvictus
